          }
        },
        "story-text-1": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Brightside Dental was founded by Dr. Elena Rhodes with a mission to make modern dentistry accessible, comfortable, and — dare we say — enjoyable. After years of working in corporate dental chains, she wanted to build something different: a practice where patients are people, not numbers.</p>",
            "size": "base"
          }
        },
        "story-text-2": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>A decade later, Brightside has grown into a team of three dentists and a dedicated support staff, serving thousands of families across Midtown Manhattan. The philosophy hasn't changed: listen carefully, explain clearly, and treat gently.</p>",
            "size": "base"
          }
        }
      },
